summary: Check help messages
description:
    A couple of oneline examples showing how simple shell
    tests can be written directly in the discover step. The
    last one demonstrates a custom script in given directory.
discover:
    tests:
      - name: /help/main
        test: tmt --help
      - name: /help/test
        test: tmt test --help
      - name: /help/plan
        test: tmt plan --help
      - name: /help/smoke
        test: ./smoke.sh
        path: /tests/shell
